Naby Keita is back at Melwood after receiving a negative COVID-19 test result and being cleared to begin training and playing again, with Jurgen Klopp hopeful the No.8 can feature in Amsterdam. #awlfc [lfc]<br />
<br />
Klopp: &ldquo;Naby trained yesterday, so that&rsquo;s very positive. He looked very good yesterday in training, to be honest. But I don&rsquo;t know how he looks today, how he reacted &ndash; that&rsquo;s much more important then. So, we will see.&quot;

